titleInfo.subTitle: STIPULATION AND ORDER MODIFYING RELEASE BOND as to Armando Solis signed by Judge Gregory G. Hollows on 1/23/06 ORDERING that defendant Armando Solis's release shall continue on the terms previously set by the magistrate judge with the following modification: the $100,000 secured by Shelly Solis's real property located at 12729 Honcut Road in Marysville, CA is hereby SUBSTITUTED with the defendant's parents' home located at 2692 Pear Street in Live Oak, CA. The secured bond and filed deed of trust shall be filed with the order. Clerk is directed to release any liens filed against Shelly Solis's real property located at 12729 Honcut Road in Marysville, CA and to RECONVEY the real property to Ms. Solis. (Caspar, M) Modified on 1/25/2006 (Caspar, M).
